Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.54,0:01:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姆斯壮少将和雷文中将失踪的事情有关？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能性很大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.32,0:01:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她不会笨到留下证据
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管他 我们的工作是掌握这个要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.24,0:01:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁那个女狐狸被中央都市的那些老虎围住的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见 少将阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.45,0:02:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你居然在中央勤务
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使了什么门路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.45,0:02:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这难道不是实力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:15.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛头小子 挺会说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.51,0:02:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天来这里有什么事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被大总统阁下叫来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.44,0:02:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能有一阵子回不了北方了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回不去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.69,0:02:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 请务必一起吃顿饭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你请客吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.23,0:02:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃到让你破产为止也可以的话 我可以接受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么吃饭就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 胆子和钱包都很小的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为交换 送您点花怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央都市有很多不错的花店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.85,0:02:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:02:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 阿姆斯壮少将
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说说关于雷文中将失踪的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来无法隐藏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.37,0:03:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到阁下这样的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然会把那种草莽的人放在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以把他做了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要那种人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留着那种大嘴巴的家伙对阁下没有任何好处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.31,0:03:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷文中将对你说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不死的军团
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家的由来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及阁下的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各种没问他的事情 都告诉我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在听了那些话之后还接受了传讯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:04:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 为了来取那个傻子坐的位子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思 好样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 给你一把椅子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为交换 布里克斯要塞由我的人来统治 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请自由处置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我精心培养的屈强之兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会让阁下满意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很满意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倔强地爬上来吧 人类
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不入虎穴焉得虎子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少将自己进了虎穴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也成了他们的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 他们不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使主人不在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是一块可以在同一意志下活动的巨大岩石
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是布里克斯要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就是熊和虎的争夺战了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}烧瓶中的小人（人造人）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里空着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如你所见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忙得如果不边吃边干就会跟不上进度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那边怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要记住的东西太多 也比较忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是阁下工作很快 让我省了不少心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.22,0:05:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟不会偷懒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来这话题会变得无趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说斯卡现在在北方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:05:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱力克兄弟也在北方吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在和我同期的露西和伊安也在北方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会告诉我各种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得今年春天北方与东方进行了次联合军事演习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃过好几次迈尔斯少佐和帕卡尼亚大尉的亏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕卡尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾达和修加也说过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈博克 奥斯卡 迈克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤尼 诺拉 查理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次说了尤尼 然后是露西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤尼来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后是斯特林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰利姆·布拉德雷是人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么不可能的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:07:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个中央都市到底会发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那边的你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.45,0:07:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.60,0:07:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 你就没有稍微惊讶什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惊讶的话 你会给我什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胆子大这点我倒是很欣赏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:42.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,23号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说号码 告诉我真名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 因为是奴隶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奴隶…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有权利和自由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为所有物被转让和买卖的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:07:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转让？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是财产 权利等交给别人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你脑子真不好使呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我会从这种人这里诞生 完全不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我血的人是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实 说是要用在实验上 取走不少…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你赋予了我血液 所以我出生在了这世上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然23号不是滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你取个名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当自己是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取个神气点的比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特奥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特奥弗拉斯托斯·博姆巴斯托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太长了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 太长的记不住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为脑子不好使
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.15,0:08:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说我脑子不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就叫 冯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:09:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冯·霍恩海姆怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.09,0:09:02.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冯·霍恩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个能记住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拼法是…对了 你会读书写字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会那个也能干活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奴隶的工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想要自由和权利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想无法获得作为人类的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作奴隶完结一生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就和这气闷的烧瓶中是一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我给予你知识吧 冯·霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫你什么才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烧瓶中的小人 叫我人造人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.69,0:10:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世间万物 由一而生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终归为一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 一就是全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全由一出
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全中含一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一如果不包含全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都化为无
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经是位了不起的链金术师了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没有走出助手的领域
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.47,0:10:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离主人的水平还差远了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你赋予了我知识
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.63,0:10:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在才过上了好生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也很感谢主人的信任
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天和谁结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有家庭也不再是梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类真是不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:11:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不那样通过交流才进行繁殖的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,种族便不能存续了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说繁殖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从你的角度看也许很傻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家庭什么的 同伴什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那些东西里存在幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们人类
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你的幸福是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢 不说得很奢侈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个能从这烧瓶里出去的身体就算幸福了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.20,0:11:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长生不老
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么达到权力和荣华顶端的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.56,0:11:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都会要往那个方面想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意你的言辞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是陛下的御前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你继续无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就把那个烧瓶砸碎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要破坏你们无法知道的知识源泉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:11:58.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废话就不必多说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长生不老
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能还是不能？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.71,0:12:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为衰老导致的焦躁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.25,0:12:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克塞鲁克塞斯王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.67,0:12:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我就告诉你长生不老的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么工程？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灌溉用水道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据国王的命令 要在全国张开水道网
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是克塞鲁克塞斯王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我们这些百姓的生活也想得很周到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.47,0:12:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个不留 全杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.56,0:12:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:12:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.22,0:13:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点刻上血之纹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说北方的村子被袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个不留全被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这之前是西边的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么人干的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好过份
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您期盼的链成阵终于完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.81,0:13:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就行了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 能长生不老了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.53,0:14:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国王能变得长生不老
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可以说是世纪性的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是长生不老？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.63,0:14:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说在中心的我们不会受害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,链成阵真正的中心是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所站的这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用了在我体内的你的血
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们打开了门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血脉相连的家人 霍恩海姆哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 你和我是一切的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维兰德 梅希帝鲁德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱因麦尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托尼 梅悠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁？回我一声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家的灵魂都被抽走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个身体 还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用你的血之资讯 制作了一个容器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:17:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.21,0:18:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于能用自己的身体走路了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是人造人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.93,0:18:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为给予我血的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你名字 教给你知识
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.31,0:18:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给予你不会衰老的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.19,0:18:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会衰老？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把意识集中到自己身体里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能听到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你成为不死之身而作为交换的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家所有人的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.92,0:18:43.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过有一半归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.61,0:18:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你的协助 霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍恩海姆先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:14.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到居然是爱德和阿尔的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是你 没想到是我儿子们的师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是受您照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊兹米小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.59,0:19:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊兹米 不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上给你药…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.94,0:19:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍微接触过一点医学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧 老毛病了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？这怎么会没事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西格先生 去叫一辆车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.74,0:19:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊兹米小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.41,0:20:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你见过真理了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你牺牲了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别糊弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子里的…被取走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想复活死去的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.30,0:20:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.09,0:20:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊兹米 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊兹米
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肚子被刺了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.62,0:21:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 呼吸变得轻松了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为被取走的脏器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你罪孽的证明 没办法取回
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微整理了一下你的肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把血的流向弄得顺畅了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.41,0:21:23.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊兹米小姐 你还不能倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍恩海姆 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.86,0:21:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:32.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有叫做冯·霍恩海姆这个人之形状的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.16,0:21:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.19,0:23:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哲学家之石
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.72,0:23:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天上之石
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.10,0:23:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大圣药
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.76,0:23:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就如贤者之石有着多个名字一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.40,0:23:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形状不一定是石头
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.04,0:23:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马可先生拿着的是半液体状的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.92,0:23:29.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金普利的是矿石状的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.46,0:23:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小就这么点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.19,0:23:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说蕴藏了很大的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.50,0:23:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以为是更大的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.78,0:23:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有见过比小石头的尺寸更大的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.28,0:23:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.57,0:23:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是非常大的贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.46,0:23:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计要使用数量非常庞大的人类为材料
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.66,0:23:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可能的话 还真不想见到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.94,0:24:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了得到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.92,0:24:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要付出同等的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是链金术的根本
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.15,0:24:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是人世间的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.57,0:24:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之链金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.01,0:24:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.81,0:24:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第41话 地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.17,0:24:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年追求的天真
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.30,0:24:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为了作为代价的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.05,0:00:23.42,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}无止境的旅途中  止步不前之时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.42,0:00:29.69,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}我们深深地叹气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.75,0:00:37.38,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}再次放开了紧握的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:44.81,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}但是现在已经没有什么可怕的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:52.74,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}连接心灵之间那坚固的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:58.20,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}决不会被斩断
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.25,0:01:07.93,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}继续寻求 终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.93,0:01:13.72,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}在这个地方画上句号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.87,0:01:23.01,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}悲伤与愤怒 化为力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.01,0:01:27.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}命运就在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.22,0:22:00.19,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本是没有交点的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.19,0:22:00.97,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今天也
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:05.83,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}企图夺走我们的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.46,0:22:11.41,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}即使获得了想要的东西
